# Liabilities Non Current Creditors And Accruals Amount

## identifier
de8941

## type
float

## definition
This is the value, as at the relevant date, of creditors and accruals, that are non-current, as determined in accordance with relevant accounting standards.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=credit
- name=Liabilities.NonCurrentCreditorsAndAccruals.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo1.02.06
- period=instant
